summary: This show is absolutely incredible. I originally only wanted to watch it becasue Sandra Oh (my queen) was in it and Greys...
body:
This show is absolutely incredible. I originally only wanted to watch it becasue Sandra Oh (my queen) was in it and Greys Anatomy is my world. However, this show is fantastic and I love it now not only becasue of her. It combines most of my favorite things, Greys Anatomy, murder mystery, and Europe all in one. (The fashion is also KILLER - no pun intended). This show is a must watch, and I am so excited for the next season!

** Also like those colors though … So. Good. **
